	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well...im goin to give my 2cp..<br><br>I have a lvl 47 High Elf cleric, of tunare...<br><br>Clerics are great, and at high lvls you really dont have to sit and wait for a group..<br><br>i choose the Highelf because they have a base Wisdom of 125 (if you put all points into it)<br><br>right now my cleric has a wisdom of 212.<br><br>i cant tell you which is the better race..they are all good, and fun to play in there own way.<br><br>now i want you to understand..that Clerics arent much fun at higher lvls..they are actually really boreing...BUT, when you hit 49, thats it, money!!! sit and make 5kpp in one day rezzing people.&nbsp;&nbsp;also you become master looter..and you get all the gems  (peridots the lvl 44 symbol gem is 11pp a stone, 229pp for a stack) just so you know what ur getting into...<br><br>24pp a spell..and it gets worse..but you make up for it...<br><br>if you play on the prexus server, and you have any questions for me.. ill be more then happy to help out.. =)<br><br>Enjoy !!!<br><br>~Jacey Angeltears<br>Seven Tongues of Chaos<br>Cleric of the 47th circle<br>Follower of Tunare..Mother of Norrath<br>Prexus<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
