	   <tr><td colspan=2>Scan down about 6 messages re race wise<br><br>Check out eq.castersreal.com for some of their info...<br><br>The main favorites are<br><br>Dark elf&nbsp;&nbsp;(High wisdom, excellent vision)<br>High elf  (High wisdom, good faction)<br>Dwarf     (High str and sta, good wisdom)<br>Halfling  (High dex and agi, good wisdom)<br><br>Humans and erudites have more balanced stats, but suffer from poor night vision<br><br>Gnomes have good int, middling-low starting wisdom, but can tinker...<br><br>Final thought?<br><br>Any race can make a good cleric. Pick the race that seems the best for you<br><br>Waerloga<br>Durus Stoneguard<br>Initiate of the 40th Mystery of Brell Serilis<br>Povar<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
